episode: I was prepared to do my taxes this past weekend.  I had all my documents ready.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I was prepared to do my taxes this past weekend.  I had all my documents ready.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Ah, taxes! Something unexpected came up, huh?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: No, it was a couple days before tax day.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Ah, cutting it close, huh?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Oh I don't know, I gave myself a few days buffer.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Indeed, quite prudent of you!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I had all my documents prepared too, so I was ready.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds like you were quite organized!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yes, you have to be with this stuff.  Don't want any trouble with the IRS.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Absolutely, avoiding issues is key!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It felt nice to have everything in one place.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Organization is satisfying, isn't it?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It was easy to find and sort through.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's efficient!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I was able to do all my taxes in under 2 hours.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Impressive!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Plus I got them all filed electronically and submitted.  Within a few hours, I got an email saying they were accepted.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Splendid, everything went smoothly!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Then, I saw my refund was deposited in my account a day later!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Marvelous! So quick!
